{"lemma":"إِبْرِيسَمِ","slug":"إِبْرِيسَمِ","root":"NTWS","root_slug":"NTWS","root_link":"/words/roots/NTWS","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2271"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A5%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"silk","tags":["obsolete"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Persian ابریشم (abrišam)."},"ipa":["/ʔib.raj.sam/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2271","headword_ar":"اـِبْرِيسَمٌ","root":"brsm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (M, [and thus written in copies of the K,]) with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as well as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"], accord. to IAar, (M,) [and] with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iborayosamN","text_ar":"اـِبْرَيْسَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;) and [app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iboriysumN","text_ar":"اـِبْرِيسُمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] with damm to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or it has three dial. forms; accord. to ISk, it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrysim","text_ar":"ابريسِم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iboriysimN","text_ar":"اـِبْرِيسِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; others say that it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrysam","text_ar":"ابريسَم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aborayosamN","text_ar":"اَبْرَيْسَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], with fet-h; IAar says that it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iboriysamN","text_ar":"اـِبْرِيسَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"and with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":", and he says that there is not in the language an instance of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ifoEiylilN","text_ar":"اـِفْعِيلِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr, but there are instances of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ifoEiylalN","text_ar":"اـِفْعِيلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iholiylajN","text_ar":"اـِهْلِيلَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iboriysamN","text_ar":"اـِبْرِيسَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S; [but I find that in two copies of that work, and in the L, this passage is mutilated; for it runs thus; “ISk says that it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iboriysamN","text_ar":"اـِبْرِيسَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":", and with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":",” &c.;]) or one of its dial. forms is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iboriysimN","text_ar":"اـِبْرِيسِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but ISk disallows this, [or, probably, as appears from what has been said above, we should read here, “accord. to ISk, but others disallow this,”] saying that there is not in the language an instance of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AfElyl","text_ar":"افعليل"},{"kind":"text","text":"with kesr to the [former]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"l","text_ar":"ل"},{"kind":"text","text":", but with fet-h, as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iholiylajN","text_ar":"اـِهْلِيلَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ToriyfalN","text_ar":"اـطْرِيفَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the second form is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aborayosamN","text_ar":"اَبْرَيْسَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h to those three letters; and the third is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iborayosamN","text_ar":"اـِبْرَيْسَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", and fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and IB [appears to indicate the second and third of these forms, for he] says that some pronounce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrysm","text_ar":"ابريسم"},{"kind":"text","text":"with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":", and some pronounce it with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", and with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Silk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariyrN","text_ar":"حَرِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) or, accord. to some, specially,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raw silk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [it is said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hryr","text_ar":"حرير"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrysm","text_ar":"ابريسم"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hr","text_ar":"حر"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or dressed silk; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrysm maTobuwx","text_ar":"ابريسم مَطْبُوخ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh and Msb in that art.:) or stuff wholly composed of silk: or of which the woof is silk: (Mgh in that art., from the Jema et-Tefáreek:) [and it is also said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaz~a","text_ar":"قَزَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrysm","text_ar":"ابريسم"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K in art."}],"source_refs":["M","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}